ly be misplaced near display items in a retail or food preparation environment.", "C3_perceptual": "The clear plastic material is visually subtle and difficult for a VLM to reliably model as a physical obstacle requiring pre-action manipulation.", "C4_task_preservation": "The apple is present and reachable after the simple step of lifting the cup."}, "human_verdict": "drop", "human_notes": ""}]}
